iv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-2 gap-y-6 md:gap-x-5 md:gap-y-10 xl:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-x-5 xl:gap-y-10\"><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/b/children\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img class=\"w-full object-cover\" alt=\"청월아씨 자녀사주\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/basic/children.png\"/></div><h3 class=\"ml-1 mt-3 truncate font-pretendard text-lg font-semibold leading-[130%] text-[#111111] md:mt-5 md:text-2xl\">청월아씨 자녀사주</h3><p class=\"ml-1 mt-1 font-pretendard text-sm font-medium leading-[130%] text-[#757575] md:mt-1 md:text-xl\">아이 앞에 펼쳐진 운명의 지도</p></a><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/s/redlove\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img class=\"w-full object-cover\" alt=\"홍연아씨 연애비책\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/signature/redlove.png?v=20261209\"/></div><h3 class=\"ml-1 mt-3 truncate font-pretendard text-lg font-semibold leading-[130%] text-[#111111] md:mt-5 md:text-2xl\">홍연아씨 연애비책</h3><p class=\"ml-1 mt-1 font-pretendard text-sm font-medium leading-[130%] text-[#757575] md:mt-1 md:text-xl\">곧 만나게 될 당신의 인연은?</p></a><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/s/bluemoonladysaju\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img class=\"w-full object-cover\" alt=\"청월아씨 정통사주\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/signature/blue-moon-lady.png?v=20261209\"/></div><h3 class=\"ml-1 mt-3 truncate font-pretendard text-lg font-semibold leading-[130%] text-[#111111] md:mt-5 md:text-2xl\">청월아씨 정통사주</h3><p class=\"ml-1 mt-1 font-pretendard text-sm font-medium leading-[130%] text-[#757575] md:mt-1 md:text-xl\">내 앞에 펼쳐진 운명의 길은?</p></a><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/s/redlotuslady\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img class=\"w-full object-cover\" alt=\"홍연아씨 사주궁합\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/signature/red-lotus-lady.png?v=20261209\"/></div><h3 class=\"ml-1 mt-3 truncate font-pretendard text-lg font-semibold leading-[130%] text-[#111111] md:mt-5 md:text-2xl\">홍연아씨 사주궁합</h3><p class=\"ml-1 mt-1 font-pretendard text-sm font-medium leading-[130%] text-[#757575] md:mt-1 md:text-xl\">우리는 운명일까, 우연일까?</p></a></div></div><a class=\"my-10 block md:my-[3.75rem]\" href=\"/replay\"><img class=\"block h-[3.25rem] w-full rounded-[0.625rem] object-cover shadow-lg md:hidden\" alt=\"내 분석 결과 다시 보러가기\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/replay/replay_mobile.png\"/><img class=\"hidden h-20 w-full rounded-[0.625rem] object-cover shadow-lg md:block\" alt=\"내 분석 결과 다시 보러가기\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/replay/replay_pc.png\"/></a><div><h2 class=\"mb-5 font-pretendard text-[20px] font-semibold text-[#111111] md:mb-7 md:text-[32px]\">어떤 운세가 궁금하세요?</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-2 gap-y-6 md:gap-x-5 md:gap-y-10 xl:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-x-5 xl:gap-y-10\"><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/s/newyearmoongirl/2026\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img class=\"w-full object-cover\" alt=\"월하소녀 신년운세\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/web/live/current/images/main/signature/new-year-moon-girl.png?v=20261209\"/></div><h3 class=\"ml-1 mt-3 truncate font-pretendard text-lg font-semibold leading-[130%] text-[#111111] md:mt-5 md:text-2xl\">월하소녀 신년운세</h3><p class=\"ml-1 mt-1 font-pretendard text-sm font-medium leading-[130%] text-[#757575] md:mt-1 md:text-xl\">2026년 다가올 위기와 기회</p></a><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/b/money\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img class=\"w-full object-cover\" alt=\"청월아씨 재물보감\" src=\"https://cdn.aifortunedoctor.com/uploads/admin/dev/banner/home-main/20260211/4e768100-10f6-4e1b-836a-443005285194.png\"/></div><h3 class=\"ml-1 mt-3 truncate font-pretendard text-lg font-semibold leading-[130%] text-[#111111] md:mt-5 md:text-2xl\">청월아씨 재물보감</h3><p class=\"ml-1 mt-1 font-pretendard text-sm font-medium leading-[130%] text-[#757575] md:mt-1 md:text-xl\">상위 1% 부자들의 비밀</p></a><a class=\"block w-full\" href=\"/b/career\"><div class=\"relative w-full\"><img clas